Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我是塞洛普
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,利維坦
